title: Native Instruments Skanner XT v1.2.0 MacOSX-R2R
description:
PlatenseSoul | R2R | 2014.03.12 | 123.1 MB

SKANNER XT is a raucous and exciting synth from the creator of REAKTOR. Part sampler, part synth, SKANNER XT offers a broad range of sounds - from big and nasty basses to celestial pads and intriguing, morphing soundscapes. 

Release Info:

Installer created by me. The original files were extracted from the Windows release of R2R.

1) Extract.
2) Mount the image and install.
3) Use it with a k'ed version of Reaktor 5.9.0 for Mac.
